      "content": "REST API for the kapa.ai answer platform. Ask retrieval-augmented questions, run threaded conversations (standard and streamed), perform semantic retrieval and search, submit feedback, and read project and analytics data. Authenticated with an X-API-KEY header.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: kapa.ai Support\n URL: https://docs.kapa.ai",
